1. Binance will launch multiple USDT perpetual contracts such as TUT/USDT and BID/USDT;
2. A smart money address cleared MUBARAK and made a profit of 517,000 US dollars;
3. He Yi: We will clean up the cheating behavior of voting for listing coins through vote washing to ensure the fairness of voting;
4. Binance updates the fiat currency trading market maker plan;
5. Australia cracks down on cryptocurrency scammers pretending to be Binance;
6. Dubai Land Department announced the launch of a pilot project for real estate tokenization, tokenizing real estate to simplify transactions;
7. Bybit CEO: 88.87% of stolen funds can still be traced, and mixer transactions have become the biggest challenge currently;
8. South Korean prosecutors raided Bithumb headquarters to investigate its suspected misappropriation of funds to purchase a personal apartment for the former CEO;
9. JPMorgan Chase CEO: The US economy is still in the "soft landing" stage;
10. Bitcoin volatility rose to 3.62%, and has risen for 14 consecutive trading days;
11. "ETH high-win rate band whale" increased its holdings of HYPE by 3.18 million US dollars in Hyperliquid;
12. Lazarus Group's address transferred 12.9 BTC, and the number of BTC holdings dropped to 13,440;
13. Binance will list Nillion (NIL) and open trading pairs.
